videos.description: Wisconsin TE Troy Fumagalli makes a great one-handed, 20-yard catch.
videos.headline: Wisconsin's Fumagalli makes great one-handed catch

videos.description: Wisonsin RB Corey Clement takes it 2 yards for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Clement goes untouched for Wisconsin TD

videos.description: Dare Ogunbowale punches it in to extend Wisconsin's lead.
videos.headline: Wisconsin punches in second TD

videos.description: Western Michigan QB Zach Terrell fakes the handoff and takes it in himself.
videos.headline: Western Michigan gets on the board

videos.description: Jazz Peavy takes the jet sweep for 51 yards into Western Michigan territory.
videos.headline: Wisconsin's Peavy breaks out for a 51-yard gain

videos.description: Western Michigan coach P.J. Fleck is pretty excited after his team gets a first-and-goal due to a reversed call on the field.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fleck pumped up about reversed call) 2017/01/02

videos.headline: Fleck pumped up about reversed call

videos.description: Western Michigan runs a complex trick play, but are only able to gain 6 yards.
videos.headline: Western Michigan runs wild trick play for short gain

videos.description: Wisconsin's T.J. Edwards picks off the pass deep in Western Michigan territory.
videos.headline: Wisconsin gets key turnover

videos.description: Alex Hornibrook finds a leaping Troy Fumagalli in the back of the end zone for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Wisconsin extends its lead on Fumagalli's TD catch

videos.description: Zach Terrell rolls out and heaves up a pass, which is caught by Corey Davis for an 11-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Western Michigan cuts into lead with 11-yard TD

videos.description: Wisconsin coach Paul Chryst talks about his team's performance in its win over Western Michigan in the  Goodyear Cotton Bowl Classic.
videos.headline: Paul Chryst proud of his team

videos.description: Wisconsin TE Troy Fumagalli talks about his performance in the Badgers' win over Western Michigan in the Goodyear Cotton Bowl Classic.
videos.headline: Fumagalli says Wisconsin a resilient group

videos.description: Wisconsin RB Corey Clement talks about what it mean to beat Western Michigan in his final collegiate game.
videos.headline: Clement enjoying the special feeling winning the Cotton Bowl
